1. *Bolnici* su uglavnom puni pacijenata tokom zimskih meseci. (Hospitals are usually full of patients during winter months.)

2. *Bolnicom* se obično upravlja direktor. (The hospital is usually managed by a director.)

3. *Bolnica* je otvorena kako bi se pružila najbolja moguća pomoć pacijentima. (The hospital was opened to provide the best possible care to patients.)

4. *Bolnice* su danas naprednije nego ikad ranije. (Hospitals are more advanced today than ever before.)

5. *Bolnice* imaju veliki broj lekara i medicinskog osoblja. (Hospitals have a large number of doctors and medical staff.)